Description:Test puzzle for replaying a draw-damage loop from the commander combo list: Niv-Mizzet, Parun plus Curiosity. Curiosity is already attached to Niv-Mizzet. Cast Opt to start the loop, then record one cycle of targeting the opponent with Niv-Mizzet's damage trigger and accepting Curiosity's draw. Repeat until the opponent is defeated.

